Class: fix
Compatible: compat
State: unknown
Version: 1.4.0i1
Date: 1461155743

This fixes a problem on certain distributions where that feature is not currently
working in <tt>curl</tt>. The option <tt>-1</tt> forces TLS - which is the only
safe protocol in our days, anyway.
